{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"rzzcdejvex294ozjezmr7n3","title":"Log Structured Merge Tree","desc":"","updated":1662347805055,"created":1662346854641,"custom":{},"fname":"programing.datastructure.tree.log-structured-merge-tree","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"af9e3ab87812082b36d69d072334eed7","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"programing.datastructure.tree.log-structured-merge-tree","id":"rzzcdejvex294ozjezmr7n3","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"database.no-sql","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":12,"offset":108},"end":{"line":8,"column":31,"offset":127},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"database.no-sql"}}],"anchors":{"log-structured-merge-tree-lsmt":{"type":"header","text":"Log structured merge tree (LSMT)","value":"log-structured-merge-tree-lsmt","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"overview":{"type":"header","text":"Overview","value":"overview","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"write-operation":{"type":"header","text":"Write operation","value":"write-operation","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"update-existing-keys":{"type":"header","text":"Update existing keys","value":"update-existing-keys","line":27,"column":0,"depth":2},"delete":{"type":"header","text":"Delete","value":"delete","line":31,"column":0,"depth":2},"read":{"type":"header","text":"Read","value":"read","line":35,"column":0,"depth":2},"save-disk-space":{"type":"header","text":"Save disk space","value":"save-disk-space","line":39,"column":0,"depth":2},"merges--compaction":{"type":"header","text":"Merges & Compaction","value":"merges--compaction","line":45,"column":0,"depth":2},"optimization":{"type":"header","text":"Optimization","value":"optimization","line":52,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"8rpsjfi5sisf8j7ttkx2tzb","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"log-structured-merge-tree\">Log Structured Merge Tree<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#log-structured-merge-tree\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"log-structured-merge-tree-lsmt\">Log structured merge tree (LSMT)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#log-structured-merge-tree-lsmt\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I6jB0nM9SKU\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I6jB0nM9SKU</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"overview\">Overview<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#overview\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Used for <a href=\"/notes/7kfh5gzgi0chi9t1l4mi0sd\">No SQL</a></li>\n<li>Optimized for <strong>fast writes</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"write-operation\">Write operation<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#write-operation\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Writes are batched in memory</strong> using the memtable\n<ul>\n<li>memtable: ordered by object key\n<ul>\n<li>implemented as a Balanced Binary tree</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>When the memtable reach a size, it will be sort &#x26; flush to the Sorted String Table (SSTable)\n<ul>\n<li>K-V in a sorted sequence => sequential I/O</li>\n<li>Most recent segment of the LSMT</li>\n<li>immutable</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"update-existing-keys\">Update existing keys<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#update-existing-keys\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>new entry is written to the most recent SSTable => Suspendes entries in the old SSTable</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"delete\">Delete<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#delete\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Add a <strong>marker (a tombstone)</strong> to the most recent SSTable for the object key</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"read\">Read<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#read\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Find in the Memtable => Find in the SSTable sequentially</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"save-disk-space\">Save disk space<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#save-disk-space\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Periodical merges &#x26; compact\n<ul>\n<li>delete unused</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Sorted => Fast</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"merges--compaction\">Merges &#x26; Compaction<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#merges--compaction\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The SSTables are organized into levels</li>\n<li>Strategies\n<ul>\n<li>Size Tiered Compaction: Write (Cassandra)</li>\n<li>Leveld Compaction: Read (RocksDB)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"optimization\">Optimization<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#optimization\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Summary table: skip </li>\n<li>Bloom filter: prevent searching for non existing key</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanhpp/)\n\n## Dendron\n\n- 